description: The UBS ETF – Factor MSCI EMU Total Shareholder Yield UCITS ETF sub-fund is an exchange traded fund incorporated in Luxembourg. The objective of the fund is to deliver the performance of the MSCI EMU Total Shareholder Yield Total Return Net and allow intraday trading.
name: UBS ETF - Factor MSCI EMU Total Shareholder Yield UCITS ETF (hedged to GBP) A-dis
